Cell["\<\
The real outputs of these two expressions are equivalent on the interval (-\
\[Infinity],\[Infinity]). However, when imaginary components are included, \
the outputs are only the same on the interval [-1,1].\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7576408396597133`*^9, 3.757640970025028*^9}, {
  3.757879639590542*^9, 3.7578796428357368`*^9}, {3.75788387121465*^9, 
