}, Open  ]],

Cell[TextData[{
 "The period is 210\[Pi]. This was calculated by finding the periods of the \
two pieces of the functions, cos(x/7) and ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["sin", "2"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "1858e222-c279-47b6-9436-ed1c221e0c07"],
 "(x/15). The periods are 14\[Pi] and 30\[Pi], respectively. To find the \
period of the combined function, the least common multiple of the two periods \
was calculated. This is 210\[Pi]. To confirm, we used the FunctionPeriod \
built-in function."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.757521690542184*^9, 3.7575217153797007`*^9}, {
  3.7575218870931745`*^9, 3.7575220282493896`*^9}, {3.757727874813313*^9, 
  3.7577278755755157`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b6c968cc-e1e4-4d69-9481-\
fd01503a65cb"],

